To run acceptance test:

    casperjs test acceptance.js --direct --log-level=info --url=example.com

To run action tests:

    casperjs action-submitform.js [--screenshot-path=path/to/screenshots] --url=example.com/contacts
    casperjs action-lightbox.js [--screenshot-path=path/to/screenshots] --url=example.com/gallery

To run responsive test:

    casperjs responsive.js --screenshot-path=path/to/screenshots example.com
